{"type": "article", "id": 27810, "title": "天空时钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-06T06:57:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702143951ls2MoGOZ1kbrgEzm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>你是如何理解时间的？媒体艺术家以及时计学者 Scott Thrift 将时间简化为天空的变化，设计了这款名为 Today 的时钟。Today 的时针比普通的时钟走得更慢，24 小时旋转一圈，正上方为正午，正下方则为午夜。钟面采用了源自天空的渐变颜色，给人一种舒适的视觉体验。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/scottthrift/today\">链接</a>参与众筹，根据不同的版本，价格从 88 到 158 美元不等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143949Crb3exqIsWVmiEg9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.63691932\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143949R5XObcSVU1vBpWgn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143950PSXUfB75k1RcMO30.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143950r5caPEvN1wTdWoHL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}